==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unkindly
<hw>Un*kind"ly</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Not kindly; unkind;
ungracious.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Unnatural; contrary to nature.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> ⟦ldquo⟧<xex>Unkindly</xex> crime.⟦rdquo⟧
<rj><au>Spenser.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>Unfavorable; annoying; malignant.</def>
<rj><au>Milton.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unkindred</ent>⟦br⟧
